Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.74,0:00:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooishi-san
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.75,0:00:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Because inbound recovery is expected, I have set up the Japanese content
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.55,0:00:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you please take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.70,0:00:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll take a look
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.22,0:00:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.40,0:00:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you you make the name of the star bigger?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.74,0:00:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how is the media coverage for tomorrow's supplement company launch going to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.58,0:00:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday special show about Ichiro teaching baseball to kids was great
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer equals Koushien after all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.68,0:00:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweat, mud and tears melts together under the summer sun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.75,0:00:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.39,0:00:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But Chief,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,playing sports under the blazing hot sun is kind of outdated don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.18,0:00:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the other day it was 30 degrees in the middle of the night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:00:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that my phone was broken
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.44,0:01:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Singing the school anthem to support their school at the Alps stand
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.92,0:01:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's youth for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's summer in Japan for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.32,0:01:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so too, Kirimura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.57,0:01:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it global warming? Or is it the pole shift?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.53,0:01:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember my school anthem
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.18,0:01:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that it's absurd that the temperature setting for air conditioning the whole building is the same for all floors?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.25,0:01:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It depends on the season, only during summers and winters
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your generation also watches Koushien, right Komukai?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see kids keep looking at the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.65,0:01:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.37,0:01:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's certainly a bit chilly over here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.32,0:01:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to file a complaint?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.18,0:01:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You watch Koushien, right Komukai?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.69,0:01:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,At least reply when people are talking to you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.76,0:01:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this also a power harassment, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.08,0:01:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.27,0:01:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.15,0:01:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.80,0:01:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is peaceful over here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.32,0:01:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.80,0:01:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So precious
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:02:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, it's time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.83,0:02:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,As you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.94,0:03:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,due to the wave of digitalization
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the event industry is in transition
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I want everyone to respond accordingly just like Ooishi-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Ooishi-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.41,0:03:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooishi-san is good looking, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in him at all
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.37,0:03:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooishi-kun sure is getting fat
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like Inuzuka-kun in his younger days
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.89,0:03:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just greasy back then
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.64,0:03:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They should have done this award ceremony over zoom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just the best Ooishi-san
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an interesting freshman in department 1
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody is getting assigned to be under me in department 3, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up is the joint project presentation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,department 1 proposes an Iot project in depopulated areas
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a medium-to-long-term city development project
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We will strive for regional revitalization through Iot
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.24,0:04:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Department 2 proposes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,a metaverse avatar fashion show
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.39,0:04:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A famous person's avatar will appear on the show,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can enjoy an exclusive experience
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.02,0:04:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In the metaverse that is all the rage these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.32,0:04:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What department 3 came up with is
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.45,0:04:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,a cat park where you can interact with cats
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We will prepare a number of attractions while they are playing the the cute cats
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Komukai
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.65,0:04:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I took some hot water
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.44,0:04:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I'm asking you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The joint presentation, what was that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.19,0:04:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The cat park?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.56,0:04:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.44,0:04:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Or are you guys for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We came up with a project, it's all good
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.41,0:04:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that it's not good to just come up with something to clear your quota?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.48,0:04:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about moving people and money in your head
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.12,0:04:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to give it all that you got
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Work using your own name
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay with just by getting your paycheck?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.73,0:04:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I did something to you, Asai?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You said during the entrance ceremony to do our best because we don't have that many people that enter the company at the same time
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired watching department 3
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.07,0:04:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.03,0:04:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you eavesdropping, Nakano-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:04:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I just overheard on my way to get some coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:04:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Department 3 is the only one in red
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:04:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So unpleasant
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Your project is interesting, but I just can't see it actually happening
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you evaluated your own project?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If you take what others have told you and then you tell other people as is, I'm going to punch you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay to be passionate, but do it yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.53,0:05:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Komukai
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.80,0:05:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you looking at your phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.36,0:05:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's lunch
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.72,0:05:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.32,0:05:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when you become a mass production-type person?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.24,0:05:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mass production-type?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Working under the radar,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,avoiding conflicts,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,getting your paycheck,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,looking forward to lunch all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and then posting said lunch on a SNS site that nobody sees
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.09,0:05:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's out of line
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You know just how hard the event industry is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.69,0:05:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The way things are going, there's a rumor that department 3 is getting disbanded
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that everything would be fine if I'm here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,An organization spreads those kinds of rumors from time to time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.19,0:06:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They might ask me to retire early
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.87,0:06:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll move somewhere when the time comes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to stay here forever, because it's peaceful
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.42,0:06:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Kijimura-san
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.57,0:06:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We still don't know what the future holds
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do everything that we can for our client
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Manten Nodoame's event
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't this be a DM instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.34,0:06:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our love for Manten Nodoame
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.04,0:06:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Our thoughts and feelings will reach them
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with that friend of yours, Asai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.68,0:06:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that he has a strong desire for approval
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.32,0:06:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Agreed
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.94,0:06:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakano-san
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I a mass production-type person?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.58,0:06:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,When I chill out at home
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.42,0:06:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.86,0:06:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's fun
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.32,0:06:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to be in the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:06:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The future...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.28,0:07:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Nakano-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.20,0:07:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be rich
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.37,0:07:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected from you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.32,0:07:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to maintain the status quo as much as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something that you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A good hair dryer
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Club activities?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.31,0:07:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in the dance club during middle school
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.56,0:07:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and I didn't join any clubs in high school
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.63,0:07:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You like to dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone was doing it at the time
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.69,0:07:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What about college?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Literature department, majoring in German literature
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.64,0:07:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What attracted you to German literature?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the easiest department to get into
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.78,0:07:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me your war story
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I never missed a day of cram school
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the election?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have an interest, but I do vote
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.95,0:07:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you buy your clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought them all at the train station
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a mass production-type person
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.69,0:07:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A mass production-type Riko with no peaks nor valleys
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's even worse that what Asai said to me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stop working
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.09,0:07:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.42,0:07:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, can I do my own work now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The one from the second division, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, please help her
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.18,0:07:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A rare store festival
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that there used to be a lot of independent stores like electric, stationary and candy stores in town,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but they're all now few and far between, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.35,0:08:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This project aims to show off the uniqueness of such retro spaces
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing the trophies at the hardware store gets my blood pumping
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.55,0:08:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,For me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.56,0:08:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved the toy store
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt like everything in that store was waiting for me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.19,0:08:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart was racing every time I passed it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything was sparkling
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I was interested in robots, plastic models or dinosaurs, but
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.08,0:08:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I was nervous everytime I passed it for some reason
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.12,0:08:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I was excited looking at dolls or transforming sticks
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A mass production-type where she has lost her dreams, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't say that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, if you see such a store, go take a look, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since when you become a mass production-type person?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.44,0:08:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:08:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Komukai
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:08:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you making a fool of yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.49,0:09:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.42,0:09:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you excited?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Is excitement necessary for adults?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard what he said to you earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.09,0:09:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something that can get lost into?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing pokemon or watching videos
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.41,0:09:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like that so much that it makes your nose bleed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.67,0:09:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go wild, so much so that it will make your nose bleed
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.32,0:09:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go wild
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.60,0:09:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Go wild?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he mean by "go wild"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.36,0:09:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What is a mass production-type?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Toy store
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.95,0:09:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that there's a toy store in this place
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Model store?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Last shooting
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be surprised, I'm terribly sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.97,0:11:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.74,0:11:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times have I told you to turn on the lights once it gets dark, Yassan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.56,0:11:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not here because I'm looking for something
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like plastic models?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I never build one before
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.87,0:11:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your first time, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I just entered this store on a whim
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,On a whim...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.03,0:11:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.23,0:11:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take your time and choose a plastic model
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You have plenty of time
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.15,0:11:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:11:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mass production-type
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.84,0:12:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In the anime Gundam, it is a mobile suit that is used by the enemy force, the Zeon army
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Main mass production-type Zaku
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.44,0:12:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaku
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You know Gundam, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the name
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Zaku is a mass production-type, it has no discerning trait and people say that it's a background character
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only for combat, but it is also used for security, large-scale construction and reconnaissance
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.50,0:12:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In short, they serve as the foil to other distinct and strong mobile suits
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.69,0:12:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Foils...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But, one reason that Gundam is a long beloved series
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of these type of mass production-type appeared on screen
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So the production gives a sense of reality that there are ordinary soldiers that fought in wars
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,For on land or for underwater use
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The charm of a mass production-type is that it has a lot of variations
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and because of that, people are still going crazy over it to this day
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.57,0:12:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The charm of a mass production-type...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:12:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to build it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:12:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.58,0:13:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to build this over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.02,0:13:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's free of charge
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to pay for it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.83,0:13:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rare to see someone chose an old kit
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Old kit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the start of everything
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.36,0:13:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the start of Gunplas
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Komukai Riko
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.66,0:13:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then Riko-san
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko is off
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.15,0:13:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the box
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing that the parts are attached to is called a runner
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.28,0:13:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But it only has one color
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to paint it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.78,0:13:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Paint?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.93,0:13:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get started
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You cut the part that connects the parts to the runner, they are called gates
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about the order this time
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.88,0:13:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,just start cutting wherever you want
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Released
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it to life
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Carefully
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a 1/144 mass production-type Zaku
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.08,0:14:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That is an old type of plastic model called old kit
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.38,0:14:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All the parts must be glued together
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The age range was changed from 8 years old and up to 15 years old and up
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.36,0:14:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lot of information
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.36,0:15:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up is gluing the parts
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.07,0:15:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The newer models uses snap fit and doesn't use any glue, but
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.49,0:15:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,it is needed for old kits
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.85,0:15:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's glue for plastic models
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.79,0:15:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time using it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I put too much glue on it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.16,0:15:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, you can smooth it out later
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:15:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Smooth it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.19,0:16:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.89,0:16:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I broke it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing that you can do about number 41
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiemi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You continue building it, Riko
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.09,0:16:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No honorifics?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We wait until the glue is dry
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we're going to smooth out the excess glue
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.64,0:17:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to do the head
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,0:18:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's time to paint the Zaku
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.58,0:18:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually you paint it while looking at the box
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.72,0:18:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Failure is sometimes a gift
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You can fix it to your hearts content
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,To my hearts content...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do anything with plastic models
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.32,0:18:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no rule that says you have to paint it accordingly
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:19:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, you'd temporarily build it first before painting it to figure out the spots that is hard to paint over
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll teach you about that later
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The old kits...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mass production-type Zaku
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.19,0:19:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Give birth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Give birth
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.16,0:19:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt like sound disappeared for a moment
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.87,0:20:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of the amygdala that is located deep within your brain was working
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.28,0:20:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That part of the brain is usually tired because of information overload, but
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When you can concentrate on just one thing, you feel energized and is able to concentrate
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.63,0:20:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You were in the zone
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm going to get a nose bleed
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.40,0:20:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.63,0:20:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So funny
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.02,0:20:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They say that they can see the story just by looking at a masterpiece plastic model
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine is clunky so I don't see the story at all, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.56,0:20:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.89,0:20:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.78,0:20:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really cute
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Fondness is a form of love
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your very own mass production-type Zaku that you build yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.44,0:20:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My very own mass production-type Zaku
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.11,0:21:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.35,0:21:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.52,0:21:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen, Riko?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.07,0:21:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to deliver this documents
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.16,0:21:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You were too aggressive
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.64,0:21:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Think it over and don't worry about it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.78,0:21:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Komukai-san
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.35,0:21:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,About the cat park that you presented during the joint presentation
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.04,0:21:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not a lot of people who can pull it off
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.31,0:21:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.33,0:21:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I was scolded, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.60,0:21:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,department 3 might come to an end soon
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.88,0:21:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A problematic person from department 1 is coming your way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.26,0:22:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Asai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.83,0:22:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember what you told me the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.80,0:22:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Komukai Riko, a mass production-type person
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.93,0:22:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.34,0:22:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying with a straight face...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.69,0:22:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.28,0:22:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Komukai...
